import React from 'react'
import {BrowserRouter, Route, Routes} from 'react-router-dom'


import Step from './components/steps/Step'

function App() {

    return (
        <>
            <BrowserRouter>
                <Routes>
                    <Route path='/:id' element={<Step />}></Route>
                    
                </Routes>
            </BrowserRouter>


        </>


    )
}

export default App
